metadata.description:
“Fallen” by Mister TW

File Type: MP4/ File Size: 30.3 MB

“This piece was inspired by the greatest fall from grace. Azraeli, once a beautiful and important angel, thought he could overthrow his Master and planned the coup with envious eyes. Before he could even try anything, the leading cherub fought and defeated him. Now banished from Heaven, he was thrown into Earth, doomed to live amongst humans forever."
- Mister TW
